HEADWORD: Lance fish
<hw>Lance" fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A slender marine fish of the genus <gen>Ammodytes</gen>, especially
<spn>Ammodytes tobianus</spn> of the English coast; -- called also
<altname>sand lance</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

